Life is Strange - A Storm is Coming! ►► http://bit.ly/1JIVHDy

Playing a game within a game today. The Magic Circle is a game stuck in Game Development Hell - and we are a QA Tester stuck inside! With our ability to hack and rewrite code will we be able to finish this broken game, or will we be trapped forever?!

Subscribe & hang out with us every day! ►► http://bit.ly/1Oo7KH9
Follow us on Twitter at @MatPatGT and #GTLive
